<number id="B5350C474C4FFFB8FB34FDFE6A6EFD8F" box="[1253,1310,540,563]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42" value="1967.0">1967</number>
), which is in 
<collectionCode id="65EC86A54C4FFFB8FE35FDDB6D48FDEC" box="[484,568,569,592]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">BMNH</collectionCode>
.
</paragraph>
